# FinFlow Mail SMTP Settings Configuration
# To use your real Gmail account to send verification OTPs:
# 1. Enable 2-Step Verification on your Google Account (myaccount.google.com).
# 2. Search for "App Passwords" and create a new 16-character App Password for FinFlow.
# 3. Rename this file to ".env" and fill in your details below.

SMTP_HOST=smtp.gmail.com
SMTP_PORT=587
SMTP_USER=your-email@gmail.com
SMTP_PASS=your-16-character-gmail-app-password
